data.description: [Seller offering $5,000 in closing costs/rate buy down with an acceptable offer] You won't be able to find better finishes and/or single-story living in another townhome like this! Enjoy this spacious and well maintained SINGLE LEVEL end unit with ZERO steps. The open floorplan offers an abundance of natural light with several upgrades: laminate floors throughout (NO carpet), neutral paint color, white modern kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a full brick exterior. The primary bedroom includes a walk in closet with oversized bathroom vanity and tile shower. Fenced private patio with additional exterior storage closet. Stackable washer/dryer to remain. Only steps away from the beautiful community pool. Designed for easy and low-maintenance living. Located in the desirable and convenient Polk Place of North Columbia!
